Package edu.unc.cs.comp524.parsers.prolog

Class PrologBaseListener

java.lang.Object
edu.unc.cs.comp524.parsers.prolog.PrologBaseListener
All Implemented Interfaces:
PrologListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
Direct Known Subclasses:
PrologListenerWithTokens
public class PrologBaseListener
extends Object
implements PrologListener
This class provides an empty implementation of PrologListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
